title: RHS Hampton Court Palace Flower Show 2017 WEB-DL.x264-JIVE
description:
RHS Hampton Court Palace Flower Show 2017




Displays at the world's biggest annual flower show. Monty, Joe and a team of experts review the diverse range of show gardens and discover how multi award-winning designer Andy Sturgeon is recycling Chelsea Flower Show gardens of the past.

Arit Anderson reveals the stories behind the conceptual gardens, and Adam Frost begins his nightly guide on how best to use plants in the design of his own garden.




Original Air Dates: 05-Jul-2017 to 07-Jul-2017
